Problem solved. I did in fact mix up the brackets. I have to start with `{` instead of `[`.

```{% module "two_column_module" path="/Events/Event Modules/Events Two Column", label="Events Two Column", 
  left_column={
    "content": [
      {
        "module_type": "text",
        "rich_text": "this is the left column",
      },
      {
